# Mission Control — environment variables
# Copy to `.env.local` and adjust. Never commit real values (code-conventions: env vars).
# Mission Control is read-only over the factory and never calls Claude, so it needs no secrets.

# --- Factory location -------------------------------------------------------
# Absolute path to the factory repo root (the folder that contains `mission-control/`).
# Optional: by default it resolves to one level up from the process cwd
# (`process.cwd()/..`), which is correct when the app runs from `mission-control/`.
# Set this only when running the app from a different working directory — e.g. tests
# or a non-standard launch. See src/lib/config.ts (resolveFactoryRoot).
# PANDACORP_FACTORY_ROOT=/absolute/path/to/panda-corp
